node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Mark Phillips on July 25, 2021 tagging @ive_ben_jamin, @l0veandpeac3, @23_is_leland, @cleanuniform, @dylanpatel4_, @dreamconvention, and @playthatjohn. May be an image of 8 people and text.

node.text:
Man what an experience this year I really can cry right now we’ve created something so amazing.. I Just feel like Dreamcon is the best con ever created I know thats a big statement but the love and genuiness at the con makes feel like almost a home or something! And every year it just gets better and better.however We could not be here without the other creators, staff and most importantly our supporters! So thank y’all Fr 😭😭😭❤️ BEST WEEKEND EVER YALL!

Pictures by @levijpg
